snippet.title: Tiger's Invasion (Telugu) | Tiger Nageswara Rao | Ravi Teja | Vamsee | Abhishek Agarwal Arts
snippet.description:
TIGER'S MENACING INVASION BEGINS 🐅
#TigerNageswaraRao 🥷 Teaser out now💥

In cinemas on October 20th 💥

#RaviTeja #Vamsee #AbhishekAgarwal #NupurSanon #GayatriBharadwaj #RenuDesai #MayankSinghaniya #AbhishekAgarwalArts

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamsee’s Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.

Cast: Ravi Teja, Nupur Sanon, Gayatri Bharadwaj and others
Writer, Director: Vamsee
Producer: Abhishek Agarwal
Banner: Abhishek Agarwal Arts
Presenter: Tej Narayan Agarwal
Co-Producer: Mayank Singhaniya
Dialogues: Srikanth Vissa
Music Director: GV Prakash Kumar
DOP: R Madhie
DI - B2H
Colorist - S. Raghunath varma
Production Designer: Avinash Kolla
PRO: Vamsi-Shekar
Marketing: FirstShow

snippet.title: 200 Pounds BIG TUNA FISH | Tuna Fish Cutting and Cooking in Village | Tuna Fish Steak Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook big Tuna fish to make fish steak recipe. In this video, we show how we cutting the giant tuna for cooking. After cooking Tuna fish meat, the fish bones and head are cooked separately by making fish curry.

Finally, we eat in the evening. The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: Boys Hostel Theatrical Trailer | In Cinemas Aug 26 | Annapurna Studios | Nithin Krishnamurthy
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Madness!  These animals are extremely stupid, wild, and dangerous. Get ready to hurt your cheek bones as these boys will take you on a roller coaster ride.
#BoysHostel - This youth crazy comedy entertainer is Kannada’s biggest blockbuster of 2023.Releasing in Telugu on 26th August, we present you the official trailer of the film. 
Boys Hostel is a one-of-its-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy’s hostel, featuring 500 + theatre talents and cameos by stars like Rishab Shetty, Tharun Bhascker Dhaassyam, Pawan Kumar, Shine Shetty & Rashmi Gautam. The film is presented by Annapurna Studios in collaboration with Chai Bisket Films. The movie is produced by Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. 
#BoysHostel from 26th August in Theatres Worldwide.

Boys Hostel is a one-of-its-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy’s hostel, featuring 500 + theatre talents and cameos by stars like Rishab Shetty, Tharun Bhascker Dhaassyam, Pawan Kumar, Shine Shetty & Rashmi Gautam. The film is presented by Annapurna Studios in collaboration with Chai Bisket Films. The movie is produced by Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. 
#BoysHostel from 26th August in Theatres Worldwide.

snippet.title: Rameshwar ji के आंसू और मुस्कुराहट में भारत की आवाज़ गूंजती है | Rahul Gandhi
snippet.description:
भारत जोड़ो यात्रा की शुरूआत से ही लोगों की बातें सुन रहा हूं, उनके दुख-दर्द पहचान रहा हूं।

अनायास एक दिन रामेश्वर जी का एक वीडियो सामने आया - एक आम इंसान, एक खुद्दार और ईमानदार भारतीय जो मेहनत से अपने परिवार का पालन करना चाहता है, मगर उनकी आंखें भरी हुईं, मजबूरी के आंसुओं से। करें तो करें क्या - एक तरफ बेरोज़गारी का गहरा कुआं, तो दूसरी ओर महंगाई की खाई।

इत्तेफ़ाक से रामेश्वर जी ने मिलने की इच्छा जताई, जिसके लिए मैं खुद इच्छुक था। सादर और सपरिवार उन्हें घर पर खाने के लिए आमंत्रित किया। कुछ बातें करनी थी उन्हें, और मुझे भी उनसे मिलकर उन्हें नज़दीक से जानने का मन था।

आर्थिक रूप से ग़रीब, मगर दिल के बहुत धनी हैं रामेश्वर जी - जितनी भी देर बातें हुईं, उनके चेहरे पर मुस्कान बरकरार रही। उन्होंने उम्मीदें टूटने के किस्से बताए, मगर साथ में ज़िम्मेदारियों का एहसास भी है। उनकी हिम्मत असल मायने में आशा की सुनहरी किरण है।  

आज, करोड़ों अन्य भारतीयों की तरह, रामेश्वर जी भी तरक्की की पंक्ति के आख़िर में खड़े हैं - एक ऐसी जगह, जहां न रोज़गार है, न महंगाई से राहत, न व्यापार के सही मौके और न ही कोई आर्थिक सुरक्षा। जब तक हर सुविधा उन तक नहीं पहुंचती, ये कदम नहीं रुकेंगे, ये सिलसिला नहीं रुकेगा, यात्रा नहीं रुकेगी।

आज़ादी का यह ख़्वाब हमें साथ मिल कर पूरा करना है!

#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra, #rameshwar

snippet.title: Chandrayan-3 | Releases Moon Photos | After Successful Process of Lander Module DE Boosting
snippet.description:
జాబిల్లి దక్షిణ ధ్రువంపై అధ్యయనం కోసం చేపట్టిన చంద్రయాన్ -3 మిషన్ లో భాగంగా  ల్యాండర్  తీసిన చంద్రుని ఫోటోలను ఇస్రో విడుదల చేసింది. ఆగస్టు 15, 17 తేదీల్లో తీసిన జాబిల్లి చిత్రాలను సామాజిక మాధ్యమాల్లో ఇస్రో పోస్ట్  చేసింది. మరోవైపు ల్యాండర్  మాడ్యూల్  డీబూస్టింగ్  ప్రక్రియను నేడు విజయవంతంగా చేపట్టిన ఇస్రో 113 కిలోమీటర్లు బై 157 కిలోమీటర్ల కక్ష్యలో ప్రవేశపెట్టింది. ఈ నెల 20న  మరోసారి డీబూస్టింగ్  ప్రక్రియను చేపట్టనున్నారు. 23వ తేదీ సాయంత్రం చంద్రుని దక్షిణ ధ్రువంపై విక్రమ్  ల్యాండర్  అడుగుపెట్టనుంది.

localized.description:
జాబిల్లి దక్షిణ ధ్రువంపై అధ్యయనం కోసం చేపట్టిన చంద్రయాన్ -3 మిషన్ లో భాగంగా  ల్యాండర్  తీసిన చంద్రుని ఫోటోలను ఇస్రో విడుదల చేసింది. ఆగస్టు 15, 17 తేదీల్లో తీసిన జాబిల్లి చిత్రాలను సామాజిక మాధ్యమాల్లో ఇస్రో పోస్ట్  చేసింది. మరోవైపు ల్యాండర్  మాడ్యూల్  డీబూస్టింగ్  ప్రక్రియను నేడు విజయవంతంగా చేపట్టిన ఇస్రో 113 కిలోమీటర్లు బై 157 కిలోమీటర్ల కక్ష్యలో ప్రవేశపెట్టింది. ఈ నెల 20న  మరోసారి డీబూస్టింగ్  ప్రక్రియను చేపట్టనున్నారు. 23వ తేదీ సాయంత్రం చంద్రుని దక్షిణ ధ్రువంపై విక్రమ్  ల్యాండర్  అడుగుపెట్టనుంది.

Gudumba Shankar is an action comedy film directed by Veera Shankar and produced by Naga Babu under Anjana Productions banner. Pawan Kalyan plays the title role in addition to writing the screenplay. The film also stars Meera Jasmine and Ashish Vidyarthi while Sayaji Shinde, Brahmanandam and Ali play supporting roles. The music was scored by Mani Sharma with cinematography by Chota K. Naidu.

snippet.title: Every Girls School On Independence Day | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows what happens in every girls school on Independence day. Scenarios like going on shopping with Indian mom to fancy dress shop , singing lessons for 15th august function in school , singing vande matram , choir selection of students , dance practices and coping up with syllabus , science teacher , other subject mam scolding and pissed off with students for missing their periods ,  dancing on desh rangila , dressing up for school function putting makeup , lots of red lipstick , rented jewellery , gudda , making bun , dressing up as different states punjab , gujrat , kashmir , west bangal , kolkata , assam , maharashtra , marathi , tamil , kanayakumari , chennia , school dance competition , making vlog in school , disscusing which class performed the best , hooting for our friends , class party on independence day bringing homemade food our cooks for us pao bhaji , cheese sandwiches , speaking on stage on democratic india , secular india , decorating class , cutting glaze paper , making chart paper on freedom fighters , rani laxmi baxi , jhansi ki rani , bhagat singh , gandhi ji , tricolor balloon decoration , making indian flag , indian mom arranging artificial jewellery for daughters school fancy dress , sewing her dress for proper fitting , maa vs beti , maa beti , our favs chinky and savitri , Patang baazi , Getting together on friend's terrace , beer bottles, Instagram photos with Indian flag , Girls doing Tricolour Eye makeup looks , School functions, 15 august dance practice in school, School life and choir singing on desh bhakhti songs , Fancy dress shopping for like Jhansi Ki Rani Mahatma Gandhi ji , Bhagat singh , freedom fighters , Getting laddoos , munch chocolate in School snacks , middle class family watching parade on Tv , forwarding Whatsapp messages of Swatantra Diwas going out for watching movie and so much more.. 
You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days .
Relive and Relish your School life.. These are the best days of school
Do share it with your friends , family , teachers , mothers , dost especially with school ones.. 
Happy Independence Day Everyone 🇮🇳
SCHOOL LIFE IS BEST. JAI HIND

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3853 | 18 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3853: Chintamani
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi is visited by an unusual patient who continues to visit him despite having no illness. Dr. Hathi urges him to eat well and sleep well in order to recover from this. The women afterward discussed their husbands' office troubles at the Gokuldham Ladies Kitty Party. Anjali complains about Taarak's boss and how he gets irritated when leaves are granted. Similarly, Babita discusses Iyer's supervisor and their issue. When Komal arrives late to the cat party, everyone is intrigued. Later, Komal mentions Dr. Hathi's strange case, which everyone finds entertaining. Watch the show to find out more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3853, 18 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Birthday Cake Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make a birthday cake recipe in tamil. This is a simple sponge cake and layered with butter cream frosting. This layered birthday cake has been decorated with bright colors.
#birthdaycake #birthdaycakerecipe #cakerecipe 

Friends, thank you so much for your kind wishes. Hope you will also try this cake recipe at home and bake them for your household birthdays. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1.25 cup Butter (250g approx)
2 cup Sugar (400g)
4 large Eggs
3 cup Maida(375g)
3 tsp Baking powder
1/4 tsp Salt
1.25 cup Milk
1 tbsp Vanilla extract
divide into 3 and bake at 350F/175C for 30 min

For Butter cream:
400g Butter
400g powdered Sugar
1/2 tsp Vanilla extract
4 tbsp Milk
Food Color

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2│Flowers│EP# 317
snippet.description:
സ്വത്തിന് വേണ്ടി ബാലുവിനെ അടിച്ച് പുറത്താക്കാൻ പോലും മടിയില്ലെന്ന് ദിയ, ലച്ചുവിനോട് പറയുന്നത് ബാലു കേൾക്കുന്നു. ഇരുവരുടെയും സംഭാഷണം പാറമട വീട്ടിൽ വലിയ പൊല്ലാപ്പുകൾക്കാണ് തുടക്കമിട്ടത്. ഹൈമവതിയും രാം കുമാറും കൂടി എത്തിയതോടെ ഇനി എന്തൊക്കെ സംഭവിക്കുമെന്ന് കണ്ടറിയണം..
'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?

#UppumMulakum2

snippet.title: Mystery of Apollo 13 Mission | Lost in Space | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
✏️ JOIN MY TIME MANAGEMENT COURSE: 
Learn how to manage time and maximize productivity in my specialised online course. 
Join here: https://academy.dhruvrathee.com
Use ‘NASA42’ for a 42% discount! Offer only valid for the first 400 people. 
Before you buy, please note that language of the course is fully English.

The story of Apollo 13, showcasing the remarkable human resilience and determination to survive against overwhelming odds. The mission began in Florida, USA, as three astronauts embarked on an audacious journey to the moon, driven by the success of previous lunar missions. However, their aspirations of moonwalking were abruptly shattered just two days later when a sudden and powerful explosion rocked their spacecraft 210,000 miles away from Earth. The ship's alarms blared, lights flashed, and the astronauts found themselves in a dire situation. Stranded far from home with limited oxygen, they were faced with an unprecedented crisis that demanded their utmost courage and resourcefulness. Did they manage to get back to earth? What was their fate? Find out in this gripping video by Dhruv Rathee.

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 vs Luna 25 - Russia and India RACE to the Moon | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
Correction: the budget of Luna 25 is 1600 crores and not 16000 crores. 


In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain how Russia's Luna25 is racing with India's Chandrayaan 3 to reach to the moon. Why has Russia launched a space mission to the moon after a long gap of 47 years? Is Russia trying to send a message to the world? And does this have any impact on Geopolitics? Let's learn and explore in this video.

#chandrayaan3 #ISRO #abhiandniyu 

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

The Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) is the national space agency of India. It was established in 1969 with the primary objective of developing space technology for peaceful purposes.

ISRO has made significant achievements in the field of space exploration. It has launched a number of satellites, including the Indian National Satellite (INSAT) system for telecommunications, television broadcasting, meteorology, and disaster warning; the Indian Remote Sensing (IRS) satellites for resource monitoring and management; and the Chandrayaan-1 spacecraft, which orbited the Moon and made significant discoveries about its surface.

In 2014, ISRO launched the Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM), also known as Mangalyaan. MOM was the first Indian spacecraft to reach Mars, and it made India the fourth country to do so.

ISRO is also planning a number of ambitious missions in the coming years, including a human spaceflight mission called Gaganyaan, a mission to study the Sun called Aditya L1, and a mission to Venus called Shukrayaan 1.

Here are some of the major milestones of India's space program:

1962: First sounding rocket launched from Thumba Equatorial Rocket Launching Station (TERLS)
1975: First satellite, Aryabhata, launched
1980: First remote sensing satellite, IRS-1A, launched
1994: First launch of the Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle (PSLV)
1999: First launch of the Geosynchronous Satellite Launch Vehicle (GSLV)
2008: First lunar orbiter, Chandrayaan-1, launched
2014: Mars Orbiter Mission (MOM) launched
2022: Chandrayaan-3 mission launched
2023: Aditya L1 mission launched
India's space program is a major driver of scientific and technological development in the country. It has also helped to improve India's disaster management capabilities and to provide valuable information about the Earth's resources. ISRO is a leading space agency in the world, and its achievements are an inspiration to many.

Some Love stories are created for your love for the same art. "Tu Aashiqui Hai Meri" is a beautiful melody composed by Queen Payal Dev and she has rendered her just so perfect vocals with the super talented Stebin Ben, who also featured in this video with the gorgeous "Doll" Niti Taylor. We sincerely hope you will like there chemistry in this video and enjoy this soothing romantic track. Do leave us comments to tell us how much you like the audio/video. Enjoy!!!!

A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. snippet.title: Ajay Devgn Threatens Murali Sharma | Singham | Movie Scene
snippet.description:
An honest and valiant policeman, Bajirao Singham, fights against injustice. However, when he encounters a corrupt politician, Jaikant Shikre, he deAn honest and valiant policeman, Bajirao Singham, fights against injustice. However, when he encounters a corrupt politician, Jaikant Shikre, he decides to teach him a lesson. #singham 

Bajirao Singham is a police sub- inspector who hails from a small town of Sawantwadi in Maharashtra. He fights against corruption with the valor of lion. 

When Kavya comes to Sawantwadi, from Goa to visit her grandparents on a vacation she is charmed by Bajirao's bold and courageous demeanor.

Everything goes well for Singham until there is a clash with a goon that eventually escalates into a full blown fight. Singham eventually gets promoted & is transferred to Goa which also happens to be the operational hub of the goon.

While this move brings Singham closer to Kavya, it also brings him in the clutches of the very same goon who is on a mission to destroy him. How Singham rises to the challenge to expose this crook and put an end to his malicious activities forms the rest of the story.

Starcast: Ajay Devgn, Kajal Aggarwal and Prakash Raj
Directed by: Rohit Shetty

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2│Flowers│EP# 316
snippet.description:
അഭിനയമോഹം തലയ്ക്ക് പിടിച്ചിരിക്കുകയാണ് രാം കുമാറിന്. ലച്ചുവും ദിയയും പലതുംപറഞ്ഞ് പിന്തിരിപ്പിക്കാൻ ശ്രമിക്കുന്നുണ്ടെങ്കിലും രാം കുമാർ രണ്ടും കൽപ്പിച്ചാണ്. ആരെയും വകവയ്ക്കാതെ അഭിനയമോഹവുമായി മുന്നോട്ട് പോകുന്ന രാം കുമാറിന് നിർദേശങ്ങളുമായി ബാലുവും ഒപ്പമുണ്ട്. ഇനി എന്തൊക്കെ സംഭവിക്കുമെന്ന് കാത്തിരുന്ന് കാണാം.

'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?

#UppumMulakum2 #BijiSopanam #NishaSarang #flowerstv

snippet.title: Surabhiyum Suhasiniyum│Flowers│EP# 341
snippet.description:
ഇപ്പോഴും സുഹാസിനി സുരഭിയോട് മിണ്ടുന്നില്ലെന്നുള്ള യഥാർത്ഥ്യം ഉൾക്കൊള്ളാനാകാതെ നിരാശയിലാണ് പ്രതീഷ്. എല്ലാം തന്റെ തെറ്റാണെന്നാണ് സുഹാസിനി വിശ്വസിക്കുന്നത് എന്ന് സുരഭിയും പറയുന്നു. തെറ്റുകളെല്ലാം തന്റെ ഭാഗത്താണ് എന്ന് തുറന്നു പറയാൻ പ്രതീഷ് തയ്യാറാണെങ്കിലും സുരഭി അത് അനുവദിക്കുന്നില്ല. എന്നാണ് ഇനി സുഹാസിനിയും സുരഭിയും തമ്മിലുള്ള പിണക്കം മാറുന്നത്? കാത്തിരിക്കാം. 
Pratheesh is disappointed as he cannot accept the fact that Suhasini is still not talking to Surabhi. Surabhi also says that Suhasini believes that everything is her fault. Pratheesh is ready to openly admit that all the mistakes are on his side, but Surabhi does not allow it. So the quarrel between Suhasini and Surabhi will change? Let's wait.

Episode 3852: Long Drive Ke Sapne
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha phones Taarak and requests that he accompany him to his shop. Taarak accepts Jetha's invitation, and the two agree to meet in the Gokuldham society. While Jetha is waiting for his companion, Taarak Bhide approaches and offers to join them. Jetha becomes immersed in his fantasy of a lengthy drive with Babita, but Bhide interrupts his daydream. Babita later arrives in her car and offers Jetha a ride. Jetha is overjoyed and rushes inside the car. Jetha receives a call from Champaklal, and he cancels the trip with Babita.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 17th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf

Sirf Tum Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 17th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star Clashiversary Challenge #3 (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
The Clash of Clans 2023 Clashiversary Event progresses to Challenge 3. The Future Queen Skin is showcased in this level designed by Yuta14. It involves a Queen Charge strategy to the Town Hall and can be tricky if you have not done it before. I did want to thank iTzu for helping me with the consistency of this method - namely how to save all of the troops until after the TH is destroyed. If you activate it too early it can end up taking down your healers. Best of luck with your 3 stars!

Episode 85: Sabse Purani Dhwani
-------------------------------------------------
Maa Adishi informs Baalveer and Benaam about the black hole. Benaam informs Baalveer that this black hole possesses extraordinary abilities to extract Maha Jadoo from Kaashvi. Baalveer resolves to go to the black hole in order to save Kaashvi from the effects of the magic. When Baalveer visits the location, he becomes disoriented and attempts to contact Benaam for assistance. Benaam is uncomfortable and ill, yet she manages to lead Baalveer to the strange blue cube. The blue cube turns out to be enormous, so will Baalveer carry it? Keep an eye out!

𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐄𝐍𝐓𝐒:

Ingredients For Peanut Barfi -
* Roasted Peanuts (भुनी हुई मूँगफली) - 250 Gm
* Sugar (चीनी) - 200 Gm
* Water (पानी) - 75 Ml
* Milk Powder (दूध का पाउडर) - 3 Tbsp
* Ghee (घी) - 1 Tbsp
* Almond (बादाम) - 8-10
* Cashew Nut (काजू) - 8-10
* Pistachio (पिस्ता) - 8-10
* Soaked Saffron Water (भिगोया हुआ केसर पानी) - 1 Tbsp
* Butter Paper (बटर पेपर) - As Required


𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
Take a tray or any tin, keep the butter paper in it, grease some Ghee, and keep it aside.
Roast the Peanuts on low heat and stir from time to time until they become crunchy. Then take them out on a plate & let them cool down. Then rub them between your palms & peel them off easily. Put them in a mixing jar & coarsely grind and make the Peanut Powder, then sieve the Peanut Powder. Put some Milk Powder & mix well. In a pan, put some Water and Sugar and make 1 string of Sugar Syrup. Then put the Peanut Powder in the Syrup gradually. Stir it continuously & make it lumps-free & thick. Then put some Ghee in it, and mix it well. At last, transfer the mixture to a greased tray & spread well. Dry roast some Almonds, Cashews & Pistachios for 2-4 minutes on a slow flame. 
In the same pan, put Sugar & cook it on medium flame till it melts. When Sugar gets melted, put roasted Dry Fruits & mix them well. At last, put Saffron Water & cook for a  while. Then immediately after put the caramelized mixture on the Peanut mixture & spread well. Keep it set overnight at room temperature. Then take it out on a plate and cut it into pieces & enjoy! In this way, super soft and tasty Peanut Chikki/Mithai/ Barfi will get ready at home.

snippet.title: Bhide के Scooter पर चढ़ गए सभी Gents | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Revisit The Journey
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Tapu Sena executed their plan to hide Gogi. The missing news of Gogi spread like wild fire amongst the other members of the society. All of them started to find him. Later, when they were unable to do so, all of them decide to lodge a police complaint. Stay tuned to get your daily dose of laughter.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 268
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

Bhide के Scooter पर चढ़ गए सभी Gents | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Revisit The Journey

About Puthiya Thalaimurai TV
Puthiya Thalaimurai TV (Tamil: புதிய தலைமுறை டிவி) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on August 24, 2011. Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favor or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organization or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
 
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of weekend programmes.
 
The channel is promoted by Chennai based New Gen Media Corporation. The company also publishes popular Tamil magazines - Puthiya Thalaimurai and Kalvi.

snippet.title: 1 कप पोहा से 10 मिनट में बनाए खस्ता कुरकुरा नाश्ता जो पूरे 2 महीने तक खाए /Masala papdi
snippet.description:
Siri Rs 20 /- mein tayyar karein 1/2 kg Masala Papdi…1 Cup Pohe se Sirf 10 minute mein ban jata hai…aur pure 2 marine ise kha saktein …ekdum kasta kurkura nashta hai…jisse aap sham ke shamay garma-garm Chai ke sath khaye …Khasta Nashta…Store upto 2 months …Tea time Snacks…Masala Papdi

Ingredients
1. Flattened Rice  1 Cup
2. Gram Flour 1/2 Cup
3. Water 1 tbsp
4. Refined Oil 1 tsp
5. Cumin Seeds 1/2 tsp
6. Asafoetida 1/4 tsp
7. Turmeric Powder 1/4 tsp
8. Red Chilli Flakes 1 tsp
9. Black Sesame Seeds 1 tsp
10. Coriander Leaves 1/4 Cup
11. Garam Masala 1/4 tsp
12. Dry Mango Powder 1/2 tsp
13. Salt as per taste

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 36 Teaser - 17th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast: 
Anmol Baloch - Abeer
Hamza Sohail - Hannan
Mohsin Abbas - Hamza
Sakina Khan - Amal
Fazila Kazi - Farah
Hiba Aziz - Sara
Erum Akhter - Mahrukh
Ayesha Gul - Amina
Sabiha Hashmi - Zubaida
Akber Islam - Aijaz
Zia Gurchani - Faraz
Salma Asim - Noreen
